{"tid":2499341,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"東鐵綫列車隧道內撞限速牌　服務一度延誤","createTime":"2021-04-21T23:10:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-22T00:53:19.000Z","uid":271829,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c5dd14bb7fec1d25ba50a2e139345620c4ba29af","tid":2499341,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T23:10:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/63Dhq99_EMufwX0ZkW5yELkxrwI=/535x401/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/G63KK5JDUNCGTI32WPUY6JDKEQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F63Dhq99_EMufwX0ZkW5yELkxrwI%3D%2F535x401%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FG63KK5JDUNCGTI32WPUY6JDKEQ.jpg&h=3f3904a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有列車停在九龍塘站月台，乘客被要求離開。<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n消防亦接報趕到，並派員到月台調查。警方表示，於清晨5時38分接報，指一列列車於九龍塘站開往大圍站之間的隧道內，撞到一塊指示牌，事故中無人受傷。至清晨6時許，列車服務陸續回復正常。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵表示，初步了解懷疑列車撞到一塊鬆脫的限速牌，又指會詳細調查事件原因。<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210422/VDGUFXAVUZDYPAYPRW4O6G273M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210422%2FVDGUFXAVUZDYPAYPRW4O6G273M%2F&d=tbI6yIPhVaIexgVZB5ClndagwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=fdaab7cd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210422%2FVDGUFXAVUZDYPAYPRW4O6G273M%2F&h=4a42b65f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210422/VDGUFXAVUZDYPAYPRW4O6G273M/</a>"},{"pid":"05f75b7a789b020cf24d784e72257c535555e231","tid":2499341,"uid":142097,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T23:12:40.000Z","msg":"又可以加價"},{"pid":"ce0286a5a2e48b18c44a9ba290ae2f2a6ebaec73","tid":2499341,"uid":295688,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T23:18:13.000Z","msg":"點做到？司機定乘客伸隻手出嚟？"},{"pid":"6a94bc3eb96d89b8211a6e7cb773d6c424fa8f41